# tmux
# A terminal multiplexer for managing multiple terminal sessions.

# Start a new tmux session:
tmux

# Attach to an existing session:
tmux attach

# Detach from a session:
Ctrl + b, then d

# List all sessions:
tmux ls

# Split the window vertically:
Ctrl + b, then %

# Split the window horizontally:
Ctrl + b, then "
